Mustahil sekali.

00:21:24.780 --> 00:21:25.780
Bagaimana jika saya berkeras?

00:21:32.740 --> 00:21:35.180
Jika Ibu Permaisuri membantu...

00:21:37.140 --> 00:21:38.220
Peluang lima puluh peratus.

00:21:42.980 --> 00:21:43.820
Terima kasih, tuan.

